    <briefdescription>
<para>CRC calculation for communication protocols. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Provides CRC-8, CRC-16 (CCITT, Modbus), and CRC-32 (Ethernet). Configure SYN_CRC_USE_TABLE to trade ROM for speed: 1 = 256-entry lookup table (fast, ~256–1024 bytes ROM per variant) 0 = bit-by-bit computation (small, slower)</para>
<para>All variants support incremental (streaming) computation.</para>
<para><simplesect kind="par"><title>Usage</title><para><programlisting><codeline><highlight class="normal">uint16_t<sp/>crc<sp/>=<sp/><ref refid="syn__crc_8h_1a7f547455d6657471da9cfc954bb7e139" kindref="member">syn_crc16_ccitt</ref>(data,<sp/>len);</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
